				  lohit-bengali
Current Version :- 2.91.1

* Wed Dec 03 2014 Pravin Satpute <psatpute@redhat.com> - 2.91.1
- Resolved issue of conjuncts with matra issue #57
- Fixed issues for Lohit-Bengali for winxp

* Fri Oct 10 2014 Pravin Satpute <psatpute@redhat.com> - 2.91.0
- First release of Bengali under Lohit2 project.
- Rewritten all GSUB rules.
- Open type feature available in .fea file for easy reusability.
- Developer friendly glyphname with following AGL guidelines.
- Font Information updated in sfd.
- Support bng2 and beng open type tags.
- "copy reference" feature implemented
- Automated testing support.
- Added test and README file.
- Done with lookup writings.
- Removed 38 unwanted glyphs.

* Fri Dec 21 2012 Pravin Satpute <psatpute@redhat.com> - 2.5.3
- Dropping RFN from OFL.txt

* Thu Nov 08 2012 Pravin Satpute <psatpute@redhat.com> - 2.5.2
- resolved rendering error for UTRRS Assamese GPSO sequence 25, 28 44 and 63 for Harfbuzz 
- resolved rendering error for UTRRS Bengali GSUB sequnce 86, 88 for harfbuzz
- corrected panose values #803294

